CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 8 reads: "Thousands Attend Courier Home, Food Show...11. The impressive Heinz booth attracted hundreds while Miss Ida Mae Mauney passed out plates of delicious Heinz oven-baked beans...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ida Mae Mauney working in Heinz booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
